definitions.definition: An older spelling of Whittlesey , Cambridgeshire , England .
A local government area north of Melbourne Victoria , Australia ; in full, the City of Whittlesea .
A town within the city in Victoria .
A town south of Queenstown , Eastern Cape province, South Africa .
